name: Little Cuggles
tag_list: children-clothing, kids, clothing, accessories, tutus, shoes, dresses, onsies
overview:
Little Cuggles brings you a range of adorable and yet affordable baby and children’s clothing & accessories. We spend our time sourcing quality products which you won’t find in stores locally.

Our range of clothing which include dresses, coats, tutus, shoes, pants and shirts is not only functional but stylish as well. If you are looking for beautiful and unique clothing for your precious little one, then this is the store for you.

If there is something that you need but can’t find, then please let us know and we would be happy to source the product for you.
